  "prompt": "Who is best in Sachin, virat and dhoni?",
  "response": "Determining who is \"best\" among Sachin Tendulkar, Virat Kohli, and MS Dhoni depends on the criteria you use\u2014whether it's batting skills, leadership, impact on the game, or overall contribution to cricket. Here's a brief comparison:\n\n### **Sachin Tendulkar**\n- **Batting**: Widely regarded as one of the greatest batsmen of all time. Holds numerous records, including the most runs in Tests and ODIs.\n- **Impact**: Revered as the \"God of Cricket\" in India. Played for 24 years and inspired a generation.\n- **Legacy**: A symbol of consistency and longevity.\n\n### **Virat Kohli**\n- **Batting**: Known for his aggressive style and incredible consistency across formats. Considered one of the best chase-masters.\n- **Captaincy**: Led India to significant victories, especially in Test cricket.\n- **Legacy**: Still active but already one of the modern greats.\n\n### **MS Dhoni**\n- **Leadership**: One of the most successful captains in cricket history. Led India to World Cup wins in 2007 (T20) and 2011 (ODI), and the 2013 Champions Trophy.\n- **Finishing Skills**: Renowned for his calmness under pressure and ability to finish matches.\n- **Wicketkeeping & Strategy**: A sharp cricketing mind and a reliable wicketkeeper.\n\n### **Conclusion**\n- **Sachin** is the **greatest batsman** for his unparalleled records and longevity.\n- **Virat** is the **modern batting maestro** with his consistency and aggression.\n- **Dhoni** is the **best leader** and **finisher**, with his calmness and tactical brilliance.\n\nIt\u2019s subjective and depends on what aspect of cricket you value most! All three are legends in their own right.",
